 ('104', '3', '2', '1', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Using White Space: How Emptiness Can Give So Much to Design\",\"slug\":\"using-white-space-how-emptiness-can-give-so-much-to-design\",\"postDate\":1459007700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Craft is the CMS that\\u2019s powering Localhost. It\\u2019s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it\\u2019s made by Pixel & Tonic. We can\\u2019t wait to dive in and see what it\\u2019s capable of!<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn\\u2019t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you\\u2019re making a website.<\\/p>\",\"14\":\"\",\"2\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-17 01:12:07', '2016-07-17 01:12:07', '34e34aae-029e-406f-8a4a-27b0cf542bef'),
